- Sampling Points paramenter (s):
  - We will choose s=2*num_main_dimensions
  - See: 
    - decisions/sampling_points.png
    - decisions/df_sampling_points.RData
    - scripts/hyperparameters_tuning/divide_sampling_points.

- Number of partitions parameter (p) to get the minumum time:
  - We will choose p such that the number of observations in each partition is 4*num_main_dimensions. So, 
    p = n/(4*num_main_dimensions)
  - See:
    - decisions/num_partitions.png
    - decisions/df_num_partitions.RData
    - scripts/hyperparameters_tuning/divide_num_partition.R
